                      !ROMSplit
                      =========

This program will split a given ROM image byte wide
or word wide (four or two files).

To split an image, load the program then click the
left mouse button to open the main window.  Drag
the image to split on to this window; select the
desired split option then drag the destination icon
to a filer window where split output will be saved
then click on Split.

A status window will apear showing the progress.

To quit !ROMSplit, click the middle mouse button on
the !ROMSplit icon on the icon bar and select the
Quit option from the menu.
